title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Local Legend 10 - Boeing 307 Stratoliner
description:
In this video we will have a look at the Boeing 307 Stratoliner which has just been released to the MSFS marketplace. First we will have a look at the liveries, weight and failures which are included. After this we will do a full review of both the exterior as well as the interior which both received a lot of attention. As last part of the video we will go through the startup procedure and takeoff with the aircraft.
